- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the computational complexity of the problem and proposes a relaxation to a convex optimization problem. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory): The paper discusses the problem of finding relations between multiple sets of variables, which is related to information theory. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses a statistical technique commonly used in artificial intelligence, and compares different methods for solving the problem. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper discusses the application of the technique to real-world data, which could include image or video data commonly used in computer vision.
